<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.6">
<l>maṉṉā vimmaṉi ca<supplied>p</supplied>piṟa  viyainīkki</l>
<l>taṉṉāk kittaṉ ṉiṉaruḷ ceyyumtalaivaṉ</l>
<l>miṉṉār mukilcēr tiruvēṅ kaṭammēya</l>
<l>veṉṉā ṉaiyeṉṉap paṉeṉṉeñ ciluḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who gives his sweet grace making [us] his [own],</l>
<l>Having removed this impermanent human birth,</l>
<l>My elephant who dwells on Tiruvēṅkaṭam with lightning-filled clouds,</l>
<l>My father is the one in my heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
